author: wn.com
title: France Regrets Russia Summoned Envoy Over Aviation Incident
text: French ministries of defense and foreign affairs said in a joint statement Monday that they regretted that Moscow had summoned the French ambassador to Russia over an aviation incident which had taken place in the French airspace. Meanwhile, Moscow has officially apologized. ...
